<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5936">مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ الْمُنْكَدِرِ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/119">وَإِبْرَاهِيمَ بْنِ مَيْسَرَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«صَلَّيْتُ الظُّهْرَ مَعَ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> بِالْمَدِينَةِ أَرْبَعًا، وَبِذِي الْحُلَيْفَةِ رَكْعَتَيْنِ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>